data.description: A property in the heart of West Lancaster has hit the market after 20 years. House boasts lots of natural light, carpet and laminated wood flooring through out.  There's a great size living room and family room with their fireplaces and wet bar located in the family room. It's gourmet kitchen features tile countertops, wooden cabinets, and a breakfast bar area. All 3 bedrooms are of comfortable size and are located upstairs and 1 bedroom downstairs. It's Master Suite, has a walk-in closet , plenty of room for storage, and large accommodating bathroom. The property has a spacious backyard for a kids playground set and a possible built-in BBQ , perfect for those summer gatherings. The property also features 2 car garages, for parking 3 vehicles. Home is located near the Quartz Hill neighborhood area, close to the 14 FWY and shopping centers. Don't miss on checking out this Diamond in the rough. Property needs some TLC.
